## 📋 Additional Information

### About This Project
**AI Healthcare Risk Prediction & Clinical Decision Support System**

This project is an open-source initiative to provide AI-powered healthcare risk prediction tools for the medical community. We believe in making healthcare AI accessible, transparent, and beneficial for all.

